'''阴唇黏合'''、'''阴唇黏连'''（{{lang|en|Labial fusion,  labial fusion, labial adhesion, labial synechiae, labial agglutination, labial adherence, gynatresia, vulvar fusion, vulvar synechiae}}）<ref name=fleischer>{{cite book|title=Textbook of Pediatric Emergency Medicine|url=https://archive.org/details/textbookpediatri00flei_864|page=[https://archive.org/details/textbookpediatri00flei_864/page/n873 842]|year=2010|first=Gary R.|last=Fleisher|publisher=[[Lippincott_Williams_&_Wilkins|Lippincott Williams & Wilkins]]|first2=Stephen|last=Ludwig|isbn = 9781605471594}}</ref>，是一类[[外阴|外阴]]发育不良，女性[[大阴唇|大阴唇]]出现黏合症状<ref name=nhsdirectwales>{{cite web|url=http://www.nhsdirect.wales.nhs.uk/encyclopaedia/l/article/labialfusion/|title=NHS Direct Wales - Encyclopedia: Labial fusion|publisher=NHS Direct Wales|accessdate=2011-09-13|archive-date=2011-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927123832/http://www.nhsdirect.wales.nhs.uk/encyclopaedia/l/article/labialfusion/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

临床上通常会把婴幼儿阴唇黏连误诊为先天性畸形，然而它常由外阴、[[阴道炎|阴道炎]]引起，也可能找不到明确的致病因素<ref name=adams>{{cite book|title=The 5-minute Obstetrics and Gynecology Consult|chapter=Imperforate hymen|pages=122-123|first=Jane E. D.|last=Broecker|publisher=[[Lippincott_Williams_&_Wilkins|Lippincott Williams & Wilkins]]|year=2008|isbn=9780781769426}}</ref>。患儿常有不全性尿路阻塞。检查时两阴唇之间有一细纵条形皮肤褶皱，褶皱处用血管钳轻轻分离即可分开<ref name=belman>{{cite book|title=Clinical Pediatric Urology|pages=219-220|first=A. Barry|last=Belman|first2=Lowell R.|last2=King|first3=Stephen A.|last3=Kramer|year=2001|publisher=[[CRC_Press|CRC Press]]|isbn=9781901865639}}</ref><ref name=burge>{{cite book|title=Paediatric Surgery|url=https://archive.org/details/paediatricsurger00burg|last=Creighton|first=Sarah|chapter=Paediatric and adolescent gynaecology|pages=[https://archive.org/details/paediatricsurger00burg/page/555 555]-556|edition=2nd|publisher=[[CRC_Press|CRC Press]]|year=2005|isbn=9780340809105}}</ref>。

